descriptionHtml: A project that aims to create an intriguing background options for all the races, re-worked skill trees that offer a different way to think and customize our characters, what if -before the arrive on skyrim- we were one of the Ashlanders, or a Shadowscale from the Black Marsh, or a skilled ambassador from the imperial city? This mod offers the possibility to transform background stories in real, interesting new perks.AncientTraditions requires SkyRe_Main, but it will be relased a stand-alone version.The original Skyrim Redone is a masterpiece from T3nd0
author: Haematinon
